text: Gnathoenia albescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from Gabon.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia albescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1939
